But then you have the issue you meant before, with the column families where it is ok to contain values. I think we can modify the method in such a way that we ask for column families which contain values, like findNonEmptyColumnFamilies.  This method returns a list of column families which contain values. In the ZeebeState you can then check whether these families are the expected ones.
